body:
Prefer creating a set beforehand to avoid repeated list lookups:

```python
trainable_weights = set(layer.trainable_weights)
for weight in layer.weights:
    ...
    if self.write_grads and weight in trainable_weights:
```

Another option is to factor out the `self.write_grads` loop:

```python
if self.write_grads:
    for weight in model.trainable_weights:
       ...
```

